             was indicted for <rs id="t18240715-56-off298" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240715-56-off298" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240715-56-off298" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240715-56-cd299" type="crimeDate">8th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-56-off298 t18240715-56-cd299"></join>, a mare, price 12 l., and a chaise harness, value 2 l.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240715-56-victim529" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Bates
                  <interp inst="t18240715-56-victim529" type="surname" value="Bates"></interp>
